{"name":"Enrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API with instant alerts for Capture Forms","nodes":[{"parameters":{"rule":{"interval":[{"field":"weeks","triggerAtDay":[5],"triggerAtHour":9}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger","typeVersion":1.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"c8da6624-75e7-4fda-beb1-89aa499c0d85","name":"Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"1c4fc79d-86e9-4b4a-9e6a-5a2793054ba0","name":"page","value":"1","type":"number"},{"id":"c56cef48-a4af-4435-b0bb-cd4fa7c74ee8","name":"hasMore","value":"true","type":"boolean"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[54,400],"id":"038b4721-a23b-4a81-b584-392a968e44ef","name":"Init Cursor"},{"parameters":{"batchSize":1,"options":{"reset":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.splitInBatches","typeVersion":3,"position":[378,400],"id":"354ec634-0919-4e1b-aa06-19880570af04","name":"Page Loop"},{"parameters":{"method":"GET","url":"https://api.example.com/v1/leads","options":{"timeout":20000},"sendQuery":true,"queryParameters":{"parameters":[{"name":"page","value":"={{ $json.page }}"},{"name":"per_page","value":"50"}]}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest","typeVersion":4.2,"position":[702,880],"id":"17f68ca6-569e-44a1-ad4f-ac8ffee29d90","name":"Fetch Page from API","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"fieldToSplitOut":"data","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.splitOut","typeVersion":1,"position":[1350,880],"id":"b9a6eed3-072d-4907-9c07-d635a78ba352","name":"Split Result Items"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Normalize incoming lead records to a stable schema\nconst out = [];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const j = item.json;\n  out.push({ json: {\n    leadId: String(j.leadId ?? j.id ?? '').trim(),\n    email: typeof j.email === 'string' ? j.email.trim() : j.email ?? null,\n    source: j.source ?? 'api',\n    receivedAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n  } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[2322,880],"id":"9e75d7ed-d9f5-4114-bd8b-c40c32988d80","name":"Normalize Page Items"},{"parameters":{"compare":"selectedFields","fieldsToCompare":"leadId","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.removeDuplicates","typeVersion":2,"position":[2646,400],"id":"2428dd6f-6420-4060-aafe-c4f2bbf4c1a8","name":"Remove Duplicate Leads"},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[2970,400],"id":"8b7ebd2c-e2cd-4d2b-939b-44f69d06b13b","name":"Upsert Harvest into HubSpot","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"fieldsToSummarize":{"values":[{"aggregation":"count","field":"leadId"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.summarize","typeVersion":1.1,"position":[3294,400],"id":"38ea6852-08cb-438f-b3b9-0f80dc46f670","name":"Tally Harvest Stats"},{"parameters":{"maxItems":25},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.limit","typeVersion":1,"position":[3618,400],"id":"4e727ee4-42a6-4354-9d59-338ad8f28c4a","name":"Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"sortFieldsUi":{"sortField":[{"fieldName":"score","order":"descending"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.sort","typeVersion":1,"position":[3942,400],"id":"63cb8f57-e076-4b15-aa5f-4f6d3f97e38e","name":"Sort Leads Newest First"},{"parameters":{"keys":{"key":[{"currentKey":"id","newKey":"leadId"}]},"additionalOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.renameKeys","typeVersion":1,"position":[4266,400],"id":"d236bb87-dfb8-47e5-b4be-f4683db86a1e","name":"Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"processedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[4590,400],"id":"1ed3f03d-72a3-4cf6-a006-c7be63ce309d","name":"Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"conditions":{"options":{"caseSensitive":true,"leftValue":"","typeValidation":"strict","version":2},"conditions":[{"id":"9a4c3f29-d5bc-4d95-bc15-a699ba1866da","leftValue":"={{ $json.email }}","rightValue":"","operator":{"type":"string","operation":"notEmpty"}}],"combinator":"and"}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.filter","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[4914,400],"id":"0f5ecb10-0d4e-4de2-a99a-f4582f61df6d","name":"Guard Non-Empty email"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"94033286-5809-4352-9bee-f3ee03c028c8","name":"runAt","value":"={{ $now.toISO() }}","type":"string"},{"id":"096321da-a062-45ec-8a9e-0db53184e881","name":"itemCount","value":"={{ $input.all().length }}","type":"number"},{"id":"9318086f-a4d2-4c1b-841f-0a485eb6bd1c","name":"status","value":"completed","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,400],"id":"160f7d94-49d9-45e7-826a-71d73f78fbfc","name":"Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"resource":"contact","email":"={{ $json.email }}","additionalFields":{"companyName":"={{ $json.company }}"},"authentication":"appToken"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.hubspot","typeVersion":2,"position":[5562,400],"id":"bcbf1772-2e6f-44b7-b9a5-07aad941a880","name":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#sales","cachedResultName":"#sales"},"text":"=✅ Enrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API with instant  — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5886,400],"id":"b97312c2-7f64-466e-9116-daabc26bcd47","name":"Send Summary to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000,"onError":"continueErrorOutput"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"6c9c9e30-70d7-496b-877b-0d2368a39483","name":"failedNode","value":"={{ $json.error?.node?.name || 'unknown' }}","type":"string"},{"id":"3bfe204b-bf07-40ea-a331-92e40497d8d6","name":"errorMessage","value":"={{ $json.error?.message || JSON.stringify($json).slice(0,200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"79ecbbbe-7581-4529-90d6-ed389a99e0d4","name":"workflow","value":"={{ $workflow.name }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[5238,1420],"id":"f5de0798-f674-4dda-a13f-0f05847cb968","name":"Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#sales","cachedResultName":"#sales"},"text":"=🚨 {{ $json.workflow }} failed at {{ $json.failedNode }}: {{ $json.errorMessage }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[5562,1420],"id":"e499b48a-d0bf-47b1-ba8d-92fbb61c6feb","name":"Escalate Failure to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Weekly Schedule\n\nStarts the workflow on a timer — weekly. No input data; downstream nodes fetch what they need.\n\nNext: Init Cursor","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"d81e7ee6-30a4-0d20-ff0b-bb4154af89d4","name":"Note: Weekly Schedule"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Init Cursor\n\nShapes the item: writes `page`, `hasMore`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Page Loop","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"b1d50829-ae15-b266-0cfe-676adc135f24","name":"Note: Init Cursor"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Page Loop\n\nLoop controller — releases 1 item(s) per pass. Output 2 (loop) processes the batch, output 1 (done) fires after the last batch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Remove Duplicate Leads · ②→ Fetch Page from API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,520],"id":"b33021fb-e37c-fc30-b26d-c6343959f9d3","name":"Note: Page Loop"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fetch Page from API\n\nGET https://api.example.com/v1/leads — retries 3× with backoff on failure.\n\nPorts: ①→ Split Result Items · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 API key / bearer for the target API","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,1000],"id":"30e45a0e-9409-cc51-8e9c-c11b7af5e6d9","name":"Note: Fetch Page from API"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Split Result Items\n\nExplodes the `data` array into one item per element.\n\nNext: Normalize Page Items","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1290,1000],"id":"7ed429f5-e242-54d3-b0a8-83a6564a16ac","name":"Note: Split Result Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Normalize Page Items\n\nCustom JavaScript: Normalize incoming lead records to a stable schema\n\nNext: Page Loop","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2262,1000],"id":"8ddd0f3b-b933-803f-48a8-989eadbc5657","name":"Note: Normalize Page Items"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Remove Duplicate Leads\n\nDrops duplicates within this run (compared on `leadId`).\n\nNext: Upsert Harvest into HubSpot","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"18140596-5a92-557a-33f6-f95751f17ef1","name":"Note: Remove Duplicate Leads"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert Harvest into HubSpot\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Tally Harvest Stats · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"1c970945-84ef-e66c-b460-d45e2a0497e6","name":"Note: Upsert Harvest into HubSpot"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tally Harvest Stats\n\nGroup-by + aggregate (like a pivot table) — turns raw rows into KPI numbers.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"b5cd5dce-bffa-a371-f8e3-284b671a7ca1","name":"Note: Tally Harvest Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 25 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Sort Leads Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"0e2fe422-e7d2-1fec-72c8-a259a0a8cd31","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Leads Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Align Field Names","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3882,520],"id":"ed6c855b-59d4-5b0e-936c-dbec1a8cbe71","name":"Note: Sort Leads Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Align Field Names\n\nNormalizes field names so every source feeds the same downstream schema.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4206,520],"id":"6e165d23-1aba-fd31-876a-3ce4f8211346","name":"Note: Align Field Names"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty email","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4530,520],"id":"2b37f3ea-c6c5-17e1-4528-7896ef7230c7","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty email\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4854,520],"id":"e30aa1b1-67f9-eea4-d2e7-00ca17b1282c","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty email"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,520],"id":"c387be25-2f8a-39da-87f8-cb4a5a797bb7","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (HubSpot)\n\nhubspot — `contact` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 HubSpot private-app token","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,520],"id":"e633bbf5-c0ed-3236-19b5-adc93f7fb7b9","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (HubSpot)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5826,520],"id":"cff23e2c-946c-28b5-9082-daa137a44184","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5178,1540],"id":"5ab5d1ba-db41-8346-b6eb-1653f969151a","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[5502,1540],"id":"24b8e4d8-46a5-0e5f-092d-1de77e444a93","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Enrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API with instant alerts for Capture Forms\n\n**Pattern:** Data Enrichment · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nEnrich company profiles with HubSpot and HTTP / REST API with instant alerts for Capture Forms. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual capture forms is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Init Cursor → Page Loop → Remove Duplicate Leads → Upsert Harvest into HubSpot → Tally Harvest Stats → Cap Batch Volume → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to data enrichment without manual effort\n- Anyone automating capture forms in sales\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Scales without extra headcount\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Standardizes the process every time\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: API key / bearer for the target API; HubSpot private-app token; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"7d2ca056-d882-6601-e455-02474b8ede88","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-20],"id":"04f7962c-e716-bda0-b9d3-c5efced84381","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## ⏱ Rate limiting\n\nWork is batched and spaced with Wait so provider quotas aren't tripped. If you hit 429s, lower the batch size or raise the wait — throughput drops, reliability rises.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-20],"id":"05cb0299-5a67-b42c-3792-6a5059c19d8d","name":"⏱ Rate limiting"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🧹 Data quality\n\nDedupe/diff steps make re-runs safe: the same input twice will not create duplicate records. If you change the key fields, clear n8n's dedupe memory (node → 'Clear stored keys') before the next run.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-20],"id":"2082ed4c-9c8e-25f5-c745-026ce47ef9a3","name":"🧹 Data quality"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your capture forms process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-20],"id":"7939d190-95bf-3ff6-77d5-8072d51ef615","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Weekly Schedule":{"main":[[{"node":"Init Cursor","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Init Cursor":{"main":[[{"node":"Page Loop","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Page Loop":{"main":[[{"node":"Remove Duplicate Leads","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fetch Page from API","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fetch Page from API":{"main":[[{"node":"Split Result Items","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Split Result Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Normalize Page Items","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Normalize Page Items":{"main":[[{"node":"Page Loop","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Remove Duplicate Leads":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert Harvest into HubSpot","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert Harvest into HubSpot":{"main":[[{"node":"Tally Harvest Stats","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tally Harvest Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Leads Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Leads Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Align Field Names","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Align Field Names":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty email","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty email":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (HubSpot)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"b471bbdc-ee98-4757-a6f1-7d52c5e0dc7d","id":"FDX04461"}